@startuml
title Identity and Security Flow

actor User
participant "IAM / Identity Domains" as IAM
participant "AI Orchestrator" as ORCH
participant "AI Security Service" as SEC
participant "AI Agent Gateway" as GW
participant "Agent Executor" as EX
participant "Tool Adapter" as TOOL
database "Enterprise Resource" as RES
participant "OCI Vault" as VAULT
participant "OCI Audit" as AUDIT

User -> IAM : Authenticate
IAM --> User : ID token / SSO session
User -> ORCH : Submit request with identity context
ORCH -> SEC : Evaluate policy
SEC -> VAULT : Retrieve secrets / keys
SEC --> ORCH : Authorization decision
ORCH -> GW : Delegated execution request
GW -> EX : Scoped agent invocation
EX -> TOOL : Tool call with narrowed scope
TOOL -> RES : Access allowed resource
RES --> TOOL : Result
TOOL -> AUDIT : Emit access event
EX -> AUDIT : Emit execution event
ORCH -> AUDIT : Emit orchestration event
@enduml
